SkodaExpert Car Service
Project Description
SkodaExpert Car Service is a web application designed for managing a car service. The application allows clients to order services, mechanics to perform tasks, and managers to manage employees and services.

Key Features
Authentication and Registration:
Clients, mechanics, and managers can register and log in.
Service Management:

Managers can add, edit, and delete services.

Service Ordering:
Clients can select services, place orders, and view order history.

Employee Management:
Managers can add, edit, and delete employees.

Mechanic Tasks:
Mechanics can view their tasks and create reports.

Statistics:
Managers can view statistics on orders, services, and employees.

Installation and Running
git clone https://github.com/KirillBalashovIS122/SkodaExpert.git
cd SkodaExpert

Install Dependencies:
pip install -r requirements.txt

Database Setup:
Ensure you have Firebird installed and configured.
Update the configuration in config.py with your database settings.

Run the Application:
python run.py

Access the Application:
Open your browser and go to http://127.0.0.1:5000.

